PrecisApproval for LA CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE CHICOUTIMI in Quebec (a) to change its name to the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DU SAGUENAY; and (b) to change the boundaries of its district to the MRC du Fjord-du -Saguenay and to Ville de Saguenay excluding the territory of the Chambre du commerce et d'industrie de Ville de La Baie.
